items.title: Satellite Launch Calculator
items.desc: JavaScript app for calculating launch parameters in order to evenly space out a satelitte network with a single launch. User inputs target altitude or time period for desired network, along with total number of satellites on the launch vehilcle. Calculator outputs an elliptic deployment orbit parameters and required change of velocity required of each satellite to achieve circular target orbit. Every periapsis, a single satellite is deployed and performs circularization burn.

items.title: KSP Wiki Scraper
